{"word":"H7619 - שְׁבוּאֵל - Shᵉbûwʼêl - sheb-oo-ale' - Shebuel","slug":"H7619","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שְׁבוּאֵל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>Shᵉbûwʼêl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>sheb-oo-ale'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Shebuel"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>שׁוּבאל שׁבוּאל</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>shebû'êl shûbâ'êl</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>sheb-oo-ale'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Shebuel or Shubael = \"captive of God\" <ol><li>son of Gershom and grandson of Moses</li><li>one of the 14 sons of Heman the musician</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H7617\">H7617</a> (abbrev) or <a href=\"#/H7725\">H7725</a> and <a href=\"#/H410\">H410</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7617\">H7617</a>, <a href=\"#/H7618\">H7618</a>, <a href=\"#/H7622\">H7622</a>, <a href=\"#/H7628\">H7628</a>, <a href=\"#/H7629\">H7629</a>, <a href=\"#/H7630\">H7630</a>, <a href=\"#/H7633\">H7633</a>, <a href=\"#/H8453\">H8453</a>, <a href=\"#/H8664\">H8664</a>"}]}